window.docContents[34].resolve({"/______/#zh-intro-h007":{"contents":"在正式引用中，请将本著作引用为 Lean Developers 所著的 The Lean Language Reference。\n此外，请在引用中注明相应的 Lean 版本，即 4.31.0。\n\n","context":"Lean 参考\u0009引言","header":"1.3. 如何引用本著作","id":"/______/#zh-intro-h007"},"/____________/_______________/#zh-basictypes-bytearray-h002":{"contents":"Constructs a new empty byte array with initial capacity 0.Use ByteArray.emptyWithCapacity to create an array with a greater initial capacity.\n\nConstructs a new empty byte array with initial capacity c.\n\nAppends two byte arrays.In compiled code, calls to ByteArray.append are replaced with the much more efficient\nByteArray.fastAppend.\n\nAppends two byte arrays using fast array primitives instead of converting them into lists and back.In compiled code, this function replaces calls to ByteArray.append.\n\nCopies the slice at [srcOff, srcOff + len) in src to [destOff, destOff + len) in\ndest, growing dest if necessary. If exact is false, the capacity\nwill be doubled when grown.\n\n","context":"Lean 参考\u0009基本类型\u0009字节吞吐量\u0009API 参考","header":"20.17.1.1. 构造字节数组","id":"/____________/_______________/#zh-basictypes-bytearray-h002"},"/____________/_______________/#zh-basictypes-bytearray-h011":{"contents":"Finds the index of the first byte in a for which p returns true. If no byte\nin a satisfies p, then the result is none.The variant findFinIdx? additionally returns a proof that the found index is in bounds.\n\nFinds the index of the first byte in a for which p returns true. If no byte\nin a satisfies p, then the result is none.The index is returned along with a proof that it is a valid index in the array.\n\n","context":"Lean 参考\u0009基本类型\u0009字节吞吐量\u0009API 参考","header":"20.17.1.9. 元素谓词","id":"/____________/_______________/#zh-basictypes-bytearray-h011"},"/mvcgen-______/_______________/#mvcgen-adequacy":{"contents":"可以从纯代码调用的 Monad 通常提供一个调用运算符，该运算符将任何所需的输入状态作为参数，并返回与输出状态配对的值或某种异常值。\n示例包括 StateT.run、ExceptT.run 和 Id.run。\nAdequacy lemmas 在有关单子程序调用的语句与这些程序的 最弱前提条件 语义（由其 WP 实例给出）之间提供桥梁。\n它们表明，如果最弱的前提条件为真，则有关调用的属性为真。\n\nAdequacy lemma for Id.run.\nUseful if you want to prove a property about an expression x defined as Id.run prog and you\nwant to use mvcgen to reason about prog.\n\nAdequacy lemma for StateM.run.\nUseful if you want to prove a property about an expression x defined as StateM.run prog s and\nyou want to use mvcgen to reason about prog.\n\nAdequacy lemma for StateM.run'.\nUseful if you want to prove a property about an expression x defined as StateM.run' prog s and\nyou want to use mvcgen to reason about prog.\n\nAdequacy lemma for ReaderM.run.\nUseful if you want to prove a property about an expression x defined as ReaderM.run prog r and\nyou want to use mvcgen to reason about prog.\n\nAdequacy lemma for Except.\nUseful if you want to prove a property about a complex expression prog : Except ε α that you have\ngeneralized to a variable x and you want to use mvcgen to reason about prog.\n\nAdequacy lemma for EStateM.run.\nUseful if you want to prove a property about an expression x defined as EStateM.run prog s and\nyou want to use mvcgen to reason about prog.\n\n","context":"Lean 参考\u0009mvcgen 策略\u0009谓词变压器\u0009谓词变压器","header":"17.2.3.3. 充分性引理","id":"/mvcgen-______/_______________/#mvcgen-adequacy"},"/releases/v4.12.0/#release-v4___12___0":{"contents":"\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n","context":"Lean 参考\u0009发行说明","header":"Lean 4.12.0 (2024-10-01)","id":"/releases/v4.12.0/#release-v4___12___0"},"/releases/v4.21.0/#release-v4___21___0":{"contents":"For this release, 295 changes landed. In addition to the 100 feature additions and 83 fixes listed below there were 2 refactoring changes, 4 documentation improvements, 6 performance improvements, 2 improvements to the test suite and 98 other changes.\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n","context":"Lean 参考\u0009发行说明","header":"Lean 4.21.0 (2025-06-30)","id":"/releases/v4.21.0/#release-v4___21___0"},"/releases/v4.30.0/#release-v4___30___0":{"contents":"此版本共进行了 306 项更改。\n除了新增的 123 项功能外，\n以及下面列出的 73 个修复，\n有 17 处重构更改，\n8 项文档改进，\n19 项性能改进，\n对测试套件进行 12 项改进，\n以及 54 个其他变化。\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n","context":"Lean 参考\u0009发行说明","header":"Lean 4.30.0 (2026-05-26)","id":"/releases/v4.30.0/#release-v4___30___0"}});